casebody.head_matter:
Anthony GIBSON, petitioner,
v.
Jeffrey KILPATRICK.
No. 13-1093.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 30, 2014.
Case below, 734 F.3d 395.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted.
